OL,3,CTelecoms boss resigns weeks after
OL,4,Cleading #500 million buyout
OL,6,FThe boss of a key telecoms provider
OL,7,Fhas resigned, weeks after leading the
OL,8,F#500 million takeover of Manx Telecom.
OL,10,FDaragh McDermott had been at JT Group
OL,11,Ffor 26 years, the last five as CEO,
OL,12,Fbut says "now is the right time for me
OL,13,Fto step down".
OL,15,FHe led the firm's acquisition of Manx
OL,16,FTelecom in the Isle of Man, which was
OL,17,Fbacked by private equity firm CVC DIF
OL,18,Fand completed on Friday 15 May.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
