FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1781684279
OL,3,CTelecoms boss resigns weeks after
OL,4,Cleading #500 million buyout
OL,6,FThe move strengthened JT's grip on the
OL,7,FCrown Dependencies market as the
OL,8,Flargest network provider.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Mr McDermott adds: "It
OL,11,Fhas been a privilege to lead JT and to
OL,12,Fwork alongside such talented and
OL,13,Fcommitted colleagues.
OL,15,F"I am incredibly proud of what we have
OL,16,Fachieved together, particularly the
OL,17,Ftransformation of the business and the
OL,18,Fsuccessful acquisition of Manx Telecom
OL,19,FGroup.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1781684279
OL,3,CTelecoms boss resigns weeks after
OL,4,Cleading #500 million buyout
OL,6,F"JT has a strong future ahead and I
OL,7,Fleave with enormous confidence in the
OL,8,Fbusiness, its people and its
OL,9,Fleadership team."
OL,11,FThe company also announced that non-
OL,12,Fexecutive director Brian Fitzpatrick
OL,13,Fwill take over as Interim CEO while it
OL,14,Fcarries out the process of finding a
OL,15,Fpermanent replacement.
OL,17,FMr McDermott will work his notice
OL,18,Fperiod to support a "smooth
OL,19,Ftransition".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
