OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1781684279
OL,3,CTelecoms boss resigns weeks after
OL,4,Cleading #500 million buyout
OL,6,FChair of JT, Andy Green, adds: "Daragh
OL,7,Fhas made an exceptional contribution
OL,8,Fto JT for almost three decades,
OL,9,Fchanging the structure and strength of
OL,10,Fthe industry and helping shape JT into
OL,11,Fthe strong, forward-looking
OL,12,Forganisation it is today.
OL,14,F"Brian's extensive leadership
OL,15,Fexperience and deep sector knowledge
OL,16,Fmake him ideally placed to lead the
OL,17,Fbusiness on an interim basis."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
